    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed in mint condition, and that is a completely honest and accurate representation \u2014 this car is as close to perfect as you will find anywhere on the used market. The exterior is genuinely stunning: the paint is deep, rich, and free of any scratches, chips, swirl marks, or blemishes, and all body panels are perfectly aligned with no signs of prior repairs or paintwork. The interior is equally immaculate \u2014 every surface, seam, and material looks and feels as though it just rolled off the showroom floor, with no wear on the seats, carpets, headliner, or trim pieces. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health: the engine runs smoothly and quietly, all systems function exactly as intended, and the service history is clean and up to date. The tires have strong tread remaining, all lights and electronics work perfectly, and there are no warning lights or known issues of any kind. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a used vehicle with zero compromises \u2014 a buyer can expect to drive away with complete confidence and zero surprises.",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
